# 📌 Best Practices

- Use IAM users instead of the Root User.
- Choose the correct instance type.
- Store private keys securely.
- Enable Security Groups with minimum required ports.
- Stop unused instances to reduce cost.
- Use multiple Availability Zones for high availability.
- Regularly update your operating system.
- Monitor resources using Amazon CloudWatch.

